name: John Feldmann
bio: Producer. Musician. Father. Goldfingersinger. Lover of life.

social_posts.post_text: Thank you @ramsheadlive @starlandnj for hosting these EPIC @goldfingermusic shows! I had SO MUCH FUN!!!!

It’s always been a dream of mine to have a record company. I’m so grateful for @hatchpuppet and @nickgross for allowing my dreams to come true with @bignoise. And, of course nothing would matter without these amazing artists on the label; @theused @wearethewrecks @theveronicasmusic @modsun @goldfingermusic @girlfriends @escapethefate I love all you guys so much I had the best time at our party!! Love you all and happy holidays! 🎄🎅☕️

I had the BEST time @kswaveco. So. Fucking. Epic. Thanks @nellysmagicmoments for inviting me and @parnography for the pics! Thank you @dr_cp for the edit! So proud of you @millafeldmann for charging these gnarly waves!!
See you all at the UC Theater in Berkeley on 1/13 and The House Of Blues in Anaheim 1/14!
Thank you @tonyhawk for putting @goldfingermusic Superman in THPS. That changed A LOT for my band. So fun having you onstage at the sold out @hobanaheim. Forever grateful. #doakickflip
Thank you @modsun for including me in this beautiful masterpiece of an album. You killed it. Thank you @avrillavigne @royalandtheserpent for singing on it. @bignoise
Congrats on the record release #godsavetheteen @modsun @bignoise WHAT A NIGHT!!
A little drop of nostalgia for all you @tonyhawk Pro Skater fans … who would’ve known it all started from a video game 🤷‍♂️ 🛹

It is so emotional for me to think Toxic Positivity is the eighth album that I have done with @theused. I love this band so much. From the first time I heard them back in 2001, all way to this second. I am so proud of what we made together. I love you Bert @dan.whitesides @virtualjepha @brutalford. We are magic together. Thank you for trusting me yet again. I am forever grateful. @bignoise
Thank all you 5000 Long Islanders for ROCKING tonight! That was SO FUN!! @goldfingermusic
That was one of the best shows I’ve ever had. Thank you @hobboston for another sold out @goldfingermusic show. WE LOVE YOU BOSTON!!!! #spokesman
COUNTING THE DAYS @hobboston @goldfingermusic 7/22/23
For @johnfeldy #mashkow #mashkowtattoo #goldfinger #mashkowart
My heroes are cool. @badreligionband @mxpxpx Minor Threat.
Quebec you BROUGHT IT tonight! All 8,000  of you! Thanks for singing along 🤘
SPOKESMAN! Quebec 8/11/23
